{"tid":1679634,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"喂！今晚 (28/10) 8pm，有民間記者會！","createTime":"2019-10-28T10:11:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-28T11:32:59.000Z","uid":37525,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"b43c5ff0425ed208c8cc6332528f811dae65d91e","tid":1679634,"uid":37525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T10:11:58.000Z","msg":"第二十一次民間記者會通知<br />\n<br />\n是次記者會主題：「暴政面前 不分族裔，憑藉良心 真香港人」<br />\n<br />\n民間記者會邀請了多位長居香港的少數族裔嘉賓，分享他們參與反送中運動的經歷及感受，以及少數族裔於暴政下遭受的長久打壓。屆時民間記者會發言人及嘉賓將以中英發言。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">日期：2019年10月28日（星期一）<br />\n時間：晚上8:00</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n[size=2][b]送飯一流啦！<br />\n開住直播 同隔離枱一齊睇！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n趕唔切live 都可以之後睇重溫！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4199c2e6194e4b6338c253b8b71c78d0f2e9b57f","tid":1679634,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T10:12:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9Mfv693.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9Mfv693.jpg&h=975a7fc9&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"338c54bf32cf21e4afe805fdb39eb24f1dd4861b","tid":1679634,"uid":36088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T10:25:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4d275e5ec3fa1d317549a60d85d7273aa689064","tid":1679634,"uid":36088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T10:26:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00a7243158ac37ef1f4bb508828ef72aa8bbaed1","tid":1679634,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T10:27:06.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"2aed3794ac8db434d6dfd7fb68ab4caf66c04f84","tid":1679634,"uid":